---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout 
  title="About | Mountos codeLab"
  description="This is Mountos codeLab. A digital hackerspace for AI, ML, and game development."
>
  <div class="static-page">
    <h1>[ About_Us ]</h1>
    <div class="content">
      <p>
        &gt; Welcome to Mountos codeLab. This is our public-facing terminal and R&D lab.
      </p>
      <p>
        &gt; We focus on the intersection of several key domains. Our current research and development includes:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li><span class="highlight">AI Agentics:</span> Developing systems for managing agent trajectories and state, enabling complex task execution.</li>
        <li><span class="highlight">Machine Learning:</span> Building and converting models, with a focus on practical application and deployment.</li>
        <li><span class="highlight">Game Development:</span> Prototyping game mechanics and logic in frameworks like C++.</li>
        <li><span class="highlight">Tooling:</span> Creating pragmatic tools and interfaces, like Gradio UIs for our models.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        &gt; What you find here are raw outputs, code snippets, and live projects. It's a transparent look into our development process.
      </p>
      <p>
        &gt; Connection established. Welcome to the lab.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
<style>
  .static-page {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: auto;
  }
  .static-page h1 {
    font-size: 2.8rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    text-shadow: 0 0 8px var(--color-text);
  }
  .content {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }
  .content p {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .content ul {
    list-style-type: '>> ';
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 2;
  }
  .highlight {
    color: var(--color-link-hover);
  }
</style>
